{"tid":2186632,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警車亂Cut雙白線 累私家車主與懷孕妻險炒車","createTime":"2020-09-03T05:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T07:18:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0925146e9966e292fbe5000c4589d5bd3d6d7b6f","tid":2186632,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"近年不少駕駛者均會上載車Cam片至駕駛群組，用作討論駕駛技術。以往大多數影片均是有私家車司機涉嫌危險駕駛，被上載至網上討論，惟近年不時影片顯示有人駕駛警車時疑違反交通規例。網上瘋傳一段影片，一輛私家車前晚（9月1日）駕駛至大老山隧道收費廣場時，遇上一輛警車突然於收費站前違法越過雙白線，險些與私家車發生碰撞。事件隨即引起網民討論，不少人直斥警員涉嫌危險駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200903/S5MIVI7GAZEJBK6FCVYS7QQ5LU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200903%2FS5MIVI7GAZEJBK6FCVYS7QQ5LU%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3had04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=176b3a3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200903%2FS5MIVI7GAZEJBK6FCVYS7QQ5LU%2F&h=2408c496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200903/S5MIVI7GAZEJBK6FCVYS7QQ5LU/</a>"},{"pid":"7c87eb17ed939a6fb55cf935f54515acdc2da58c","tid":2186632,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93f5c4a2021f78c82a2411b85cb9e17d13010d8","tid":2186632,"uid":165749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"香港真係一塊褔地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fb2180cb536bc450b27c5ca2838f165cff2a30","tid":2186632,"uid":127929,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime